      "deepseek_chat_v3": "There are numerous innovative AI tools for content creation across various formats—copywriting, design, video, audio, and more. Here’s a categorized list with links to their official websites:  \n\n### **1. Text & Copywriting**  \n- **[ChatGPT (OpenAI)](https://chat.openai.com/)** – Advanced text generation for blogs, marketing copy, and brainstorming.  \n- **[Claude (Anthropic)](https://anthropic.com/)** – AI assistant optimized for long-form writing, FAQs, and analysis.  \n- **[Jasper](https://www.jasper.ai/)** – AI-powered marketing copy generator with SEO optimization.  \n- **[Copy.ai](https://www.copy.ai/)** – Specializes in ad copy, social media posts, and email drafts.  \n- **[Writesonic](https://writesonic.com/)** – AI writing assistant for blogs, product descriptions, and AI-generated art.  \n\n### **2. AI for Visual Content & Design**  \n- **[MidJourney](https://www.midjourney.com/)** – AI image generator for artistic and photorealistic designs.  \n- **[DALL·E 3 (OpenAI)](https://openai.com/dall-e-3)** – Creates highly detailed images from text prompts.  \n- **[Runway ML](https://runwayml.com/)** – AI-powered video and image editing tools (e.g., text-to-video).  \n- **[Leonardo.AI](https://leonardo.ai/)** – AI art generation with fine-tuning options for designers.  \n- **[Canva AI](https://www.canva.com/ai-tools/)** – Enhances design workflows with AI-powered templates, text generators, and media tools.  \n\n### **3. Video & Audio Generation**  \n- **[Synthesia](https://www.synthesia.io/)** – AI video generation with lifelike avatars and voiceovers.  \n- **[HeyGen](https://www.heygen.com/)** – AI video presenters for marketing and training.  \n- **[Runway’s Gen-2](https://research.runwayml.com/gen2)** – Text-to-video AI model for short clips.  \n- **[ElevenLabs](https://elevenlabs.io/)** – Ultra-realistic AI voice generation (for dubbing, narration, etc.).  \n- **[Descript](https://www.descript.com/)** – AI-powered audio/video editing with transcription and voice cloning.  \n\n### **4. AI for SEO & Content Optimization**  \n- **[SurferSEO](https://surferseo.com/)** – AI-driven content optimization based on SERP analysis.  \n- **[Frase](https://www.frase.io/)** – AI content briefs and automated research tool.  \n- **[WriterZen](https://www.writerzen.net/)** – AI-powered keyword clustering and content planning.  \n\n### **5. AI Assistants & Multi-Purpose Tools**  \n- **[Notion AI](https://www.notion.so/ai)** – AI-powered summaries, drafts, and brainstorming.  \n- **[Perplexity AI](https://www.perplexity.ai/)** – Research assistant for accurate, citation-backed content.  \n- **[PO AI (Personal Assistant AI)](https://poe.com/)** – Aggregates multiple AI models (GPT-4, Claude, etc.).  \n\nWould you like recommendations for a specific type of content (e.g., podcasts, social media, long-form articles)? Let me know, and I can refine the list!",
